{"tid":2243070,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[自家烘焙］朱古力Muffin","createTime":"2020-10-14T12:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T10:23:53.000Z","uid":132749,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cafe0da3882fd9bf11be97fb0bda209f12f90cf5","tid":2243070,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"突然想食宜個，所以就整左。<br />\n<br />\nMuffin口感紮實，無 cupcakes 咁鬆軟， 個人比較鍾意食muffin多過cupcakes 。 感覺上味道濃郁好多。<br />\n<br />\n自己整仲可以整到無咁甜，多d朱古力粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外好多會用液體菜油黎整，今次我用晒牛油黎整，香好多，但唯一唔好處係凍左會比菜油整出黎既硬小小， 食前叮返30秒就變得好鬆軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N45iRsF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN45iRsF.jpg&h=24721ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JbmRr02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJbmRr02.jpg&h=25d53ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i4Zr0k5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi4Zr0k5.jpg&h=bb1fda0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ysltj3Ncvr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYsltj3Ncvr0&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=ee82218f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ysltj3Ncvr0</a>"},{"pid":"457ef1f6c1a7d6de069b3bd46114077d6fd3c1d2","tid":2243070,"uid":272819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"牛油香好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80759529a6862f3e04f28be9e4b02684e88be680","tid":2243070,"uid":132749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"457ef1f6c1a7d6de069b3bd46114077d6fd3c1d2","tid":2243070,"uid":272819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"牛油香好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"係呀，。牛油真係正好多，但成本問題，加上食前整熱咁煩，出面好多鋪頭都唔會咁做"},{"pid":"738c7b7e8474f58d69bbfb020ddc2478e7b1e25e","tid":2243070,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"想食"},{"pid":"f0497a7a3c6935bd2798811f1c5e6fd353123cf5","tid":2243070,"uid":326470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"一定要牛油，70％黑古力先香濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3e013f8dba7169bc3172ae13875bbe0c487394","tid":2243070,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"738c7b7e8474f58d69bbfb020ddc2478e7b1e25e","tid":2243070,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"想食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T20:29:16.000Z","msg":"過黎宜邊拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31daeb7ba0090a5726e2cee27db75bd16a4e7b43","tid":2243070,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0497a7a3c6935bd2798811f1c5e6fd353123cf5","tid":2243070,"uid":326470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"一定要牛油，70％黑古力先香濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T01:37:05.000Z","msg":"我今次無落朱古力，屋企無晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf992e9737ae3c786852a190552a19251b8b7ee","tid":2243070,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0350e47790a837f09bc55a132fd0be310cadd51","tid":2243070,"uid":86457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:29:46.000Z","msg":"Muffin正<br />\n有d整到濕濕地都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f655af30acd127a